{"tid":1780934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［真黃色經濟圈]看到「中國製」就放回架上！美議員：寧願多花錢買台灣貨","createTime":"2019-12-12T18:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T09:57:02.000Z","uid":28114,"like":171,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"b128705f01887db5a09eff3723dfabeb9d0294cd","tid":1780934,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/1576046092-e203794d6a2892d97b83f0f3f5c8cb86-1392x1054.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F1576046092-e203794d6a2892d97b83f0f3f5c8cb86-1392x1054.jpg&h=ab8493bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲美國眾院外委會亞太小組共和黨首席議員約霍，資料照。（圖／美聯社／達志影像）<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦眾議院外交委員會亞太小組，國際人權日當天（ 10 日），針對中國境內政治、宗教人權等議題舉行聽證會，聚焦新疆再教育營及香港「反送中」示威，席間美國眾議員約霍（ Ted Yoho ）表示，金錢是中國能為所欲為的主因，呼籲外界應抵制中國製產品，還透露自己若看到商品上寫「中國製」的話都會拒買，寧可多花點錢購買台灣製品。<br />\n<br />\n根據《中央社》報導， 10 日的會議上，美國眾院外委會亞太小組共和黨首席議員約霍聲稱，金錢是中國能為所欲為的主因，雖然外界無法主宰或強迫中國做任何事，但仍可透過對製造商施壓，讓北京和相關企業知道，「除了中國，哪裡製造都行」（ manufacture anywhere but China ），並不是非得買陸貨不可。<br />\n<br />\n約霍還透露，自己近來外出購物，只要看到是「中國製」的商品都會擺回架上，改買台灣製造的產品，雖然因此多花了點錢，但他很開心能支持台灣這個國家，而非不顧人權的共產政權，並強調：「這是我們身為個體能做的，如果這麼做的人夠多，訊息就被傳達的更清楚。」<br />\n<br />\n約霍對台政治立場一向鮮明，除了多次於個人推特上發表挺台、挺港，及反對中國擴張的言論外， 2018 年亦曾在《台北時報》（ Taipei Times ）撰文，聲稱台灣是個繁榮的民主國家，擁有自己的經濟、教育體系、軍事、政黨、國歌和國旗，並說台灣的例子證明了自由與繁榮並非向北京政府一貫告訴其人民那樣，是相互排斥的，何況由共產黨主導的北京政府從未統治過台灣。<br />\n<br />\n約霍在該篇文章中並表示，作為美國公民，他將台灣視為獨立國家，相信大多數美國公民和政府官員也同感，美國國會將與台灣站在一起，履行美方對台的防禦性軍事供應承諾，並將努力實現與台灣的全面外交關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20191211/3812469/?from=nnfb_p&amp;utm_source=fb&amp;utm_medium=nn&amp;utm_campaign=p&amp;fbclid=IwAR1mKmLlE-Xl8_rBziMaLWM9LObdMts4u7VlNm4UWGpUC8TbAEcSRPrPjn8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20191211%2F3812469%2F%3Ffrom%3Dnnfb_p%26utm_source%3Dfb%26utm_medium%3Dnn%26utm_campaign%3Dp%26fbclid%3DIwAR1mKmLlE-Xl8_rBziMaLWM9LObdMts4u7VlNm4UWGpUC8TbAEcSRPrPjn8&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc9TLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=cd94f036\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20191211/3812469/?from=nnfb_p&amp;utm_source=fb&amp;utm_medium=nn&amp;utm_campaign=p&amp;fbclid=IwAR1mKmLlE-Xl8_rBziMaLWM9LObdMts4u7VlNm4UWGpUC8TbAEcSRPrPjn8</a>"},{"pid":"85a9855c366c69b7483056ea8b5fe74c7cecc885","tid":1780934,"uid":160650,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:45:54.000Z","msg":"身體力行 好厲害！"},{"pid":"6ad73c34d1ffde26ac7d95aa16fb5e3b517de740","tid":1780934,"uid":28114,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:46:19.000Z","msg":"一眾黃屍係完全望塵莫及<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639054909564f1fb8bac912649f5aaed31efe319","tid":1780934,"uid":227271,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:48:34.000Z","msg":"當人就應如此"},{"pid":"8b640dbc1d1806ad647f2436dc5dd37f6589c5c2","tid":1780934,"uid":286155,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:52:33.000Z","msg":"其實多啲幫襯759果類舖頭都得啦，全部外國野"},{"pid":"b9b2bb7d4a5a96a06f9f552debddee105c716d15","tid":1780934,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769c1f409b7c237c86f93c30d6a0b85a73ff24c7","tid":1780934,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6ad73c34d1ffde26ac7d95aa16fb5e3b517de740","tid":1780934,"uid":28114,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:46:19.000Z","msg":"一眾黃屍係完全望塵莫及<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\